        "text": "long life",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Rather, with A.V. marg. and R.V. text, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "years of life",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". There is perhaps a climax; not only ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "length of days",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", prolonged existence, but years of life truly so-called, life worth living. The distinction is at least suggested by the use of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "βίος",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
